bio: Alexis Rodriguez, known as 'Iron Will', inspires everyone with her unbreakable determination and strength.
Jack Thompson, 'The Beast', brings an unmatched intensity and ferocity to his training sessions.
Sophia Chang, also known as 'The Energizer', fills the gym with her endless energy and enthusiasm.
Max Patel, 'The Mindful Muscle', combines mindfulness and muscle training for a holistic fitness experience.
